    "text": [
        "Dear Robert",
        "I hope you enjoyed your birthday party last Monday but I am really sorry that I could not attended to your birthday celebration And  the main purpose of this letter is apologies for my absence without informing you .",
        "To be honest , one of my cousins , who has lived in Vancouver , called me on last Sunday that he was on the way to visit us . She requested me to received his in airport on Monday at 6:00 pm , and I could not say no to his because he came after 10 years and he is not only my cousin but also my childhood close friend , then I went to airport with my parent and come back with my cousin at 8:30 pm  . for this reason I could not be present to your birthday .",
        "Now,  I will invite you to your favorite restaurant in next Friday and I hope you forgive me .",
        "Cheers",
        "Hamidreza."
